OL,3,CWRU denies sexism is at the heart of
OL,4,Cwomen's squad contract disputes
OL,6,FThey then wrote to WRU Chair Richard
OL,7,FCollier-Keywood to voice their
OL,8,Fconcerns. He set up an internal review
OL,9,Fof the process and CEO Abi Tierney
OL,10,Ftook over the negotiations, which had
OL,11,Fpreviously been headed by Executive
OL,12,FDirector of Rugby Nigel Walker.
OL,14,FEventually, 37 female players signed
OL,15,Fprofessional contracts, which the WRU
OL,16,Fclaim are some of the most lucrative
OL,17,Fin the game.
