OL,3,CWRU denies sexism is at the heart of
OL,4,Cwomen's squad contract disputes
OL,6,FBut the Union has since apologised to
OL,7,Fits players for the way the process
OL,8,Fwas handled, however they deny that
OL,9,Fsexism was at the heart of the matter.
OL,11,F"Unfortunately, there was some
OL,12,Fmisreporting of the conclusions of the
OL,13,Freview by the Telegraph in
OL,14,Fparticular," Collier-Keywood told a
OL,15,FSenedd Committee this morning.
OL,17,F"They led with a heading of sexism and
OL,18,Fthe one thing that was not mentioned
OL,19,Fby any of the participants (in the
OL,20,Freview) was sexism.
