OL,6,F"There were many failures but they
OL,7,Fwere not to do with sex
OL,8,Fdiscrimination, as has been reported
OL,9,Fto the Board."
OL,11,FCollier-Keywood went on to explain
OL,12,Fthat the Union had not grasped the
OL,13,Freality that the women's players were
OL,14,Falso employees of the WRU, whereas in
OL,15,Fthe men's game players are contracted
OL,16,Fto their club sides.
