OL,3,CWRU denies sexism is at the heart of
OL,4,Cwomen's squad contract disputes
OL,6,FIt has emerged that players did not
OL,7,Fhave access to things like company
OL,8,Femail addresses, intranet services or
OL,9,FHR documents. This led to some players
OL,10,Ffeeling alienated.
OL,12,FThe Union has also previously admitted
OL,13,Fthat both the players and Union had
OL,14,Fvery different ideas of what was
OL,15,Fpossible in the negotiating process.
