OL,3,CWRU denies sexism is at the heart of
OL,4,Cwomen's squad contract disputes
OL,6,FCollier-Keywood admitted that it was a
OL,7,F'failure of process and leadership'.
OL,8,FHe also insisted that the WRU had
OL,9,Fplanned to create a sub-committee to
OL,10,Fmanage the running of the women's game
OL,11,Fand was adamant that had that been in
OL,12,Fplace at the start of the summer, then
OL,13,Fthese issues would not have developed.
OL,15,F"It is my responsibility as Chair of
OL,16,Fthe Board for not getting that in
OL,17,Fplace fast enough," he added.
