OL,6,FWhen asked if cultural change at the
OL,7,FUnion was about individuals or
OL,8,Finstitutional, Collier-Keywood
OL,9,Fconcluded: "It's both. Some
OL,10,Findividuals were under a lot of
OL,11,Fpressure and they did things I
OL,12,Fwouldn't normally expect them to do."
OL,14,FThe main focus of the WRU's appearance
OL,15,Fin the Senedd was to update the
OL,16,FCommittee on the implementation of
OL,17,Frecommendations from the external
OL,18,Freview that was conducted last year.
