OL,3,CWRU denies sexism is at the heart of
OL,4,Cwomen's squad contract disputes
OL,6,FThat review came off the back of
OL,7,Fallegations of a toxic culture of
OL,8,Fsexism at the Union in early 2023.
OL,10,FThe Union is in the process of
OL,11,Fimplementing all recommendations and
OL,12,Fare reporting to an external oversight
OL,13,Fcommittee.
OL,15,FBut CEO Abi Tierney warned:
OL,16,F"Transformational change is hard.
OL,17,FColleagues are really feeling that at
OL,18,Fthe moment and it will take time for
OL,19,Fthings to feel better... until we're
OL,20,Fin a stable place as an organisation."
