OL,3,CWRU denies sexism is at the heart of
OL,4,Cwomen's squad contract disputes
OL,6,FWhen asked to give assurances that
OL,7,Fmore 'bad headlines' would not emerge
OL,8,Fin the future, Tierney said: "It would
OL,9,Fbe unfair for me to say that we won't
OL,10,Fever have anymore (bad) headlines
OL,11,Fagain. I wish I could promise you. But
OL,12,FI will absolutely work my hardest with
OL,13,Fmy team for it not to happen."
OL,15,FA draft of the review of the recent
OL,16,Fcontract negotiations is currently
OL,17,Fwith the players for ratifying. When
OL,18,Fthe players and other participants are
OL,19,Fhappy that their words have been
OL,20,Faccurately represented, then it will
OL,21,Fbe released to the public.
